             was indicted for <rs id="t17991030-54-off305" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17991030-54-off305" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17991030-54-off305" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17991030-54-cd306" type="crimeDate">20th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-54-off305 t17991030-54-cd306"></join>, seven cast steel mill-bills, value 3s. 6d. and an iron winch, value 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991030-54-victim533" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Hatch
                  <interp inst="t17991030-54-victim533" type="surname" value="James Hatch"></interp>
