                     <interp inst="t17991030-54-person540" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am foreman to 
               <persName id="t17991030-54-person541">
                  James
                   Hatch
               <interp inst="t17991030-54-person541" type="surname" value="Hatch"></interp>
