                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-54-defend531 t17991030-54-punish312"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
